\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {III}{\ignorespaces Performance on Standard IEC/IEEE~60255-118-1 Scenarios [RMSE / Peak Error (Hz); mean $\pm $ std, Monte Carlo $N=30$]. SOGI-FLL: corrected FLL adaptation law; Ramp result is outside loop bandwidth (type-1 loop, no steady-state RoCoF tracking). IpDFT: Hann window, Jacobsen complex spectral interpolation~\cite  {Quinn1994}; grid search selects $N_c\!=\!2$ cycles for Ramp (33\,ms) and $N_c\!=\!10$ for Step/Mod (167\,ms). TKEO, RLS, VFF-RLS, and PI-GRU excluded (divergence or off-scale error).}}{5}{table.caption.4}\protected@file@percent }
